long_desc.thetext:
Another thing that slows this is that method MylarContextManager.hasContext() is calling File.exists() twice:

	public boolean hasContext(String path) {
		File contextFile = getFileForContext(path);
		return contextFile.exists() && contextFile.length() > 0;
	}

First on the dir (inside getFileForContext(path)) and second - on the file itself. It will speed things at least twice if you would eliminate check on the directory when called from hasContext() method (i.e. move getting actual file name into a separate method).

